Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to WWDC.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great to be back in San
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jose, the heart of Silicon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Valley and right down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,from Apple and our new campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 15 years since we held
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the developer conference in San
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jose and an awful lot has
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one thing that hasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,changed is our commitment to the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,developer community and our
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ability to do amazing things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be the best and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,biggest WWDC ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year, we host WWDC to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,bring Apple engineers and our
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,amazing developers together on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,our collective mission to change
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm pleased to tell you, the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Developer community has
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,never been more vibrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We now have 16 million
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,registered developers in the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,program around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And we added three million last
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,year alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got 5300 developers here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,this morning, our largest group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have attendees this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from 75 countries across the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's truly a worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have the most student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,developers with us this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, one of our youngest is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,here this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His, his name is Yuma Sorianto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from Australia and he's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,just 10 years old.
