Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,six and he already has five apps
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,on the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Yuma yesterday and I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,wait to see what he's going to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplish next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And while we've got some great
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,up and coming developers like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuma, we got some that got a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of a later start, Masako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako Wakamiya is just 82 years
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,old and she's from Japan and she
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,published her first app earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,this year.
