Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,yet, there is still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give them a big round of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
