Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,our four incredible platforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course as you know each of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,them stem from the same core
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,technology, but each is uniquely
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed and designed for the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,best experience for where they
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep pushing these platforms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,forward giving you, the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,developers, powerful tools and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunities to change the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this developer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,conference is so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we have a lot to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do mean a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm dispensing with the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,updates other than to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple is doing great.
