Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's get right into it and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start with tvOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We recently introduced the TV
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,app on Apple TV, iPhone and iPad
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to create the easiest way to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,discover and enjoy your TV
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,content from across your video
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,channels all in one convenient
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We launched it with support from
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,just a handful of video channels
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but now, we have 50 partners
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,integrated into the TV app.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, we're really thrilled
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to announce that Amazon is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,coming--
