Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Castle" and so much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We are so pleased to welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazon to Apple TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
