Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,really quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very excited to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,introduce watchOS 4 today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This furthers the areas that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,people love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It also introduces new ways to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,make the watch more personal to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with watch faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Apple Watch is great for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly glancing at information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And many people are using a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,watch face like this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, you need to choose what
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,information shows up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example weather, calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and workouts, or maybe you'd
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,like to look at the date and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,reminders and sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The information that you like to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,see actually varies based on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,time and your location and your
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,routines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we could actually show
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you a selection of information
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that you might need
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Siri is becoming more and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,more a proactive assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing what information you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,need when you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've created a new watch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,face, which is powered by Siri
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the new Siri watch face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it automatically displays
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the information that's most
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,relevant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can also access Siri by
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,tapping on the new complication
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,on the top left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And it automatically displays
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,this information with the same
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,type of intelligence we've
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,applied on iOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're using machine learning to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,adapt automatically based on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,your routines and the apps that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you use when you use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the morning, I might see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for example, can you time in my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,first meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I rotate the Crown, I can
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,see more information from Siri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, reminders or even
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,photo memories from the same
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,time last year or maybe from
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,this location.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And throughout the day, whenever
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you raise your wrist, the face
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,will dynamically update with the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,information for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example at noon, I might
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,see a reminder to make a call
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and I might get a pass to a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,flight that I'm taking that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, relevant passes in Wallet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,can appear here right in the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,face including from third party
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, at the end of the day, I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,might see what time the sun is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,going to set and also, I can get
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,access to controls I tend to use
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the home app at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is an intelligent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,proactive assistant right on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the new Siri face on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, sometimes you might like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of less information and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,more graphics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the soul of the new
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaleidoscope face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It displays a beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,symmetrical pattern that slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,changes throughout the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can rotate the Crown and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get this kind of trippy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,effect whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's multiple styles you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,can choose from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example if you use a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,photo like this, you can create
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a variety of Kaleidoscope
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the new Kaleidoscope
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Mickey and Minnie have been
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a big hit on Apple Watch and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,more characters have been
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,working to find their way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm really excited to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,welcome Woody, and Jessie and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Buzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to be right at
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,home inside the watch and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,there's so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And whenever you raise your
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,watch with the Toy Story Face,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to see a variety of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,vignettes kind of like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of hijinks going
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,on in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are three really lively
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,new faces in watchOS, Siri face,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaleidoscope and Toy Story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's talk about Activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Watch has already been
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,helping many people improve
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,their health and fitness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And Activity is one of the most
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,frequently used apps on the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In watchOS 4, Activity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,notifications are more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,personalized to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be "Close Your Rings"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might start off each day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with some inspiration by
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,receiving an update like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This lets you know if you're
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,close to accomplishing an
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,achievement or what you can do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to match yesterday's goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are all personalized
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And as part of the smarter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,coaching, we're also introducing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,monthly challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And these challenges are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,designed to help you either beat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or repeat something that you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplish or came close to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,doing and they're all achievable
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're based on your
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,real history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And like every great coach, we
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,want to celebrate your success
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so we've added a little bit more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,fun when you close your rings or
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,earn an achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get smaller celebrations
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for everyday successes and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,bigger celebrations for harder
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach milestones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we've also enhanced the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Workout App to be even easier to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,use and more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with the new UI where
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,quick start is right up front,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you can just tap and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And customers have really loved
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the new swimming capabilities in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Siris too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're now enhancing the pool
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,swim workout with auto-sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So just by taking a rest at the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,edge of the pool, it'll
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically mark each set of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,swimming that you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the end, you'll even get
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,your distance for each stroke
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,type and your pace for each set
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We also are creating-- It's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,great, pool swim thing is very
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also created some custom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,motion and heart rate algorithms
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for a new workout type called
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,High Intensity Interval
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is one of the most
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,popular workouts in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So we know it's going to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,favorite for a lot of you when
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you start using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you like to do more than
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,one workout in a row, it's now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,super easy to just swipe over
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,during a current workout and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,then add another one by pressing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the plus button.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You just press plus and I can
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,continue with another workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, I might do outdoor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,cycling here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just tap and I continue, super
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,easy now to do multiple workouts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in a single session.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, many people are doing the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,workouts indoors at a gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you use gym equipment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it has data the Apple Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have and the watch has
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,data the gym equipment doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you end up with numbers like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,calories and distance that don't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,quite match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So in watchOS 4, we've come up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with a great solution to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're enabling for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,time two-way data exchange in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,real-time with gym equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll be able to simply tap
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your Apple Watch, on an NFC
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,reader on the gym equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your watch will automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,launch the Workout App and you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,can connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then your heart rate is read
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,by the watch and sent to the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And data like incline and speed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is sent from the equipment to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,your watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you start and stop the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,workout in your gym machine, it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,does the same thing on your
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, all the information
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,matches, it's much easier and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a lot more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is being supported by
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the largest gym manufacturers in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the world, provided about 80% of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,equipment in gyms today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And Apple Watch-enabled
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,equipment will be rolling out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,starting this fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's talk about music.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Watch paired with AirPods
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,has really become a magical
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And where redesigning the music
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,app and watch makes this a
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,really great experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With the new music app, we're
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,going to automatically sync
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,music for you based on what you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,love to listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example, it'll
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically get your Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Music mixes like new music and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,favorites freshly updated on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,your watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And the app simply presents some
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful album art and playlist
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,images and you can just navigate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,by rotating the Digital Crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get the album you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you can just tap and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can easily play your
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,music now and we support
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,multiple playlist and music on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the watch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So your music that you love is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be ready when you are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and making Apple Watch and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,AirPods a truly magical
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,listening experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the new music app.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To give you a quick demo of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,watchOS 4, please welcome Vera
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Carr from the Watch and Health
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Engineering team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing I want to show
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you is the new doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can now vertically scroll
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,through my recently used apps
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,like the new music app.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the doc makes finding the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,apps I'm looking for easier than
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's look at the new
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligent Siri watch face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in the morning, I could see
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,things like the weather for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,today and my upcoming events.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Later today, I'm heading back to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,San Francisco to see my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the afternoon, the Siri
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,face will proactively update to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,tell me how long it will take me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we're going to see the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,new "Alien" movie, which I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,super excited about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No one spoil it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For any content in the Siri
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,face, I could tap directly into
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the app for more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here for example, the Siri face
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,has my ticket so tonight, I can
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,just raise my wrist and with one
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,tap, they'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Siri face also shows me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,timely content like photo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,memories and news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a news headline picked
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,for me by the brand new news app
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,now available on Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the app, I can view stunning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,photos, glance at top news
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,stories throughout the day and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,save them for later to be read
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,on my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also integrated our new
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Activity coaching notifications
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,directly into the Siri face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when it's near the end of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,your day or you're close to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,closing your rings, our coach
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,algorithms will tell you how
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,much you need to walk to get
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,your move goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a lot of nervous pacing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,before this so now, I just need
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to take a 16-minute walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's close those rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've added something new here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in Workout that's really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Music instantly gets me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,motivated and now in watchOS 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can pick a playlist that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically starts with my
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Music ]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I'm in a workout, I can
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly swipe to the left and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,control my music right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,These are only a few of the new
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,features in watchOS 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for you to try it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to Kevin to tell you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Terrific job, Vera.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot more coming in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,watchOS 4 including, for
