Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,also use as a blinking safety
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,light when you're doing an
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,evening run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a lot, lot more happening
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we of course have a number
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of updates that enable great
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,apps by developers in watchOS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,including more support for apps
