Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,faster app responsiveness and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,some new UI capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're also now supporting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,native Core Bluetooth on the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,watch, which is going to enable
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences for apps that work
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,with small devices around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example, continuous
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,glucose monitoring, directly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,from Dexcom sensor to your
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,watch, or a Zepp Tennis, which
