Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're still on the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, lots of new possibilities
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,here for watchOS.
