Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Developer preview is available
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,today so you can get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a free upgrade for
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone across all watches this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's just some of what's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,coming in watchOS 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please welcome Tim back to the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thanks, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Cheering Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,WatchOS 4 is a great update.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's talk about a product
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that in many ways is the heart
