Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And to tell you about what's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,next with macOS, please welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Craig Federighi, Craig.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's talk about macOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, our current release of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,macOS, of course, is macOS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sierra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Sierra brought Siri and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Pay to the Mac let you put
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your documents and your desktop
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in the cloud and even let you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,unlock your Mac automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,using the watch on your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, people are loving Sierra
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and we love it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we wanted to spend this year
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,perfecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the question is, what
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,do we call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So we enlisted once again our
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.71,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,crack marketing team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They were giddy to hop in their
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,mini bus and this time, venture
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,east, deep into the Sierras but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,this time, ascending its highest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they finally came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,they had a name they said felt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,really, really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's my privilege to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,announce for you today, macOS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,High Sierra.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we talked to the guys and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we said there might be-- this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,might be misconstrued but they
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,assured us this name is fully
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.77,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, High Sierra is all about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,deep technologies that provide a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,powerful platform for future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,innovations on the Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But we couldn't help ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we also added some refinements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And it starts with Safari.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Safari is known for its
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,efficiency and it's a legendary
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,battery life but safari is also
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,incredibly fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we benchmarked Safari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.67,0:23:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,on the same hardware running
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,macOS and Windows with all the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,popular browsers and Safari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,smokes them in benchmark after
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,benchmark, JetStream,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Speedometer, MotionMark.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Safari tops them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Safari is the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,world's fastest desktop browser
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with High Sierra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And Safari's domination
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,continues with the new modern
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,version of JavaScript,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ECMAScript 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see Safari delivers 80%
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,faster performance than Chrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in addition to being
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,tremendously fast, Safari also
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,helps give you a serene browsing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you know, sometimes you go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:23:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to read an article and instead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of finding something to read,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.23,0:23:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:23:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Music ]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just some loud audio and video
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that autoplays and disrupts your
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,whole reading vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now, don't worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,because we have autoplay
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.35,0:24:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,blocking in Safari.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Safari detects the sites that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't be playing video and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.50,0:24:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,puts you in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.53,0:24:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can always push play.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Safari is also key in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.77,0:24:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,respecting your privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, have you ever had this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,experience where you go to buy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.98,0:24:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,something on the web and you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.42,0:24:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,even complete the purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.79,0:24:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like everywhere you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,go on the web, it just follows
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.96,0:24:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.71,0:24:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It kind of feels like you're
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.79,0:24:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,being tracked and that's because
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.65,0:24:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.02,0:24:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No longer, because Safari has
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.08,0:24:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Intelligent Tracking Prevention.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.52,0:24:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Safari uses machine learning to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.29,0:24:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,identify trackers, segregate the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:24:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,cross-site scripting data, put
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.00,0:25:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it away, so now, your privacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,your browsing history is your
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.96,0:25:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,own.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.32,0:25:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about blocking ads, the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.86,0:25:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,web behaves as it always did,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.82,0:25:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but your privacy is protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I want to talk about some
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.26,0:25:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,refinements to Mail and it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.77,0:25:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,starts with search.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.41,0:25:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So in addition to providing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.35,0:25:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,searches based on recency,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.62,0:25:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,search in Mail is now using
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.49,0:25:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spotlight to identify your top
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.30,0:25:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.56,0:25:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the message you're looking
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for is almost always right there
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.25,0:25:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.50,0:25:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're into using Mail in
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.85,0:25:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,full-screen, well now, we
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.29,0:25:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,support Split View for your
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.12,0:25:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,compose window.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.89,0:25:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great way to compose
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.80,0:25:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.52,0:25:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.65,0:25:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mail is more efficient than
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.86,0:25:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.15,0:25:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It actually uses 35% less disk
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.74,0:25:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,space for storing your mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.68,0:25:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, probably our biggest area
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.60,0:25:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of refinement in High Sierra is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.83,0:25:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.01,0:25:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now-- Yeah, photos has some
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.21,0:25:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,great new organization and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.67,0:25:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,editing tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.28,0:25:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a persistent sidebar and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.45,0:25:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a new view that has all your
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.23,0:25:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,imports in chronological order.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.44,0:26:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And in any view up here on the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.27,0:26:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,upper right, you can filter by
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.71,0:26:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,your keywords, by your
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.69,0:26:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,favorites, by just media types
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.00,0:26:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,like video so it's really easy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.89,0:26:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to get to just what you're
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.85,0:26:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.31,0:26:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also improved faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.58,0:26:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It recognizes far more faces
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.25,0:26:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically using advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.63,0:26:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,convolutional neural networks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.02,0:26:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you put effort into
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.92,0:26:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,categorizing and naming people,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.59,0:26:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,well, that's now synchronized
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.18,0:26:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically across all your
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.69,0:26:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.52,0:26:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we also have some great
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.49,0:26:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,enhancements to editing inside a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.96,0:26:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.25,0:26:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see here on the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.16,0:26:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,right-hand side, all of your
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.45,0:26:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,editing tools array.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.50,0:26:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are bunch of great new
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.67,0:26:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,ones, including Curves which
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,allows you to fine-tune the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.64,0:26:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,color and contrast in your
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.07,0:26:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,image.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.94,0:26:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And Selective Color will teach
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.62,0:26:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you modify color in a selective
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.08,0:26:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,range.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.05,0:26:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think you're going to like
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.88,0:26:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,this one because if you like to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.57,0:26:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,do edits in a ProTool like
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.64,0:26:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pixelmator or Photoshop, well
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.50,0:26:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,now, when you punch out to that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.28,0:26:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,other editing tool, all of your
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.64,0:27:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,edits automatically synchronize
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.30,0:27:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,right back to your photo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.56,0:27:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,library.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.52,0:27:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.67,0:27:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Apple pioneered printed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.52,0:27:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,books.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.33,0:27:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on projects, you construct
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.28,0:27:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,right inside of the photo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.12,0:27:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,application.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.03,0:27:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we're opening this up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.87,0:27:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to third parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.46,0:27:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to offer some
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.43,0:27:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,amazing new printing services,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.75,0:27:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,full-framed wall, mounted
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.05,0:27:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,photos, and even publishing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.64,0:27:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,websites, all based on projects
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.60,0:27:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,right inside of photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.47,0:27:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are some quick
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.52,0:27:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,refinements but I want to return
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.90,0:27:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to the main story now and that's
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.02,0:27:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,technology, this-- because we've
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.46,0:27:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,gone deep on the fundamentals,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.51,0:27:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,data, video and graphics.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.41,0:27:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it comes to data, the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.37,0:27:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,fundamentals are in the file
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.33,0:27:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,system.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.27,0:27:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the Mac File System has its
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.10,0:27:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,roots actually, HFS from 30
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.02,0:27:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.75,0:27:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a lot has changed since
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.12,0:27:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.40,0:27:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a lot of flash drives or
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.98,0:27:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,storage is a billion times
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.51,0:28:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,larger and it's time for more
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.65,0:28:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,modern file system.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.65,0:28:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm pleased to announce that
