Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.42,0:28:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,System to macOS as our new
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.32,0:28:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,default.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.52,0:28:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.96,0:28:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, APFS is a thoroughly modern
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.34,0:28:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,file system, 64-bit top to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.54,0:28:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.31,0:28:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe and secure with
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.80,0:28:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,built-in crash protection and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.56,0:28:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,native encryption.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.32,0:28:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's ultra responsive with
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.24,0:28:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,modern features like instant
