Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.93,0:28:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,high performance parallellized
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.69,0:28:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,metadata operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.28,0:28:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what does that really mean
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.28,0:28:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.36,0:28:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's take a look at a
