Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.42,0:29:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, H.264 has really
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.37,0:29:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,enabled the revolution of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.39,0:29:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,streaming HD video on the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.27,0:29:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.23,0:29:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But, of course, the game is
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.05,0:29:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,moved from HD to 4K and 4K high
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.84,0:29:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,dynamic range video.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.98,0:29:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a new standard to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.49,0:29:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,support this, it's H.265 or
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.72,0:29:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,HEVC.
