Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.57,0:29:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,great, preserve all the detail
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.96,0:29:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and color, and HEVC does it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.61,0:29:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,while saving up to 40% better
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.33,0:29:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,compression than H.264.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.17,0:29:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we're building in software
