Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.78,0:29:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,ProTools, like Final Cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.97,0:29:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Motion, and Compressor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.57,0:29:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I want to return to our
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.82,0:29:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,main story which is graphics and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.16,0:30:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,graphics are all about the GPU.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.09,0:30:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The GPU has been the performance
