Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.70,0:47:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a 10-core Xeon processor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.11,0:47:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.20,0:47:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we thought, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.23,0:47:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,we've gone this far, let's get
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.95,0:47:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,really nutty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.86,0:47:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to offer it with
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.98,0:47:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,up to 18-core.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.52,0:47:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.50,0:47:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a ton of compute power.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.88,0:47:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't want to stop there
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.03,0:47:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because we wanted to go really
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.03,0:47:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,big on graphics as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.94,0:47:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the iMac Pro is going to use
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.22,0:47:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,AMD's Radeon Vega graphics.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.76,0:47:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a brand new workstation
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.80,0:47:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,class graphics architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.53,0:48:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It features a completely new GPU
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.28,0:48:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,core and high bandwidth on
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.18,0:48:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,packaged memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.92,0:48:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be available with
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.86,0:48:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,up to 16 gigabytes of VRAM and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.24,0:48:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,over 400 gigabytes per second of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.48,0:48:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,memory bandwidth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.25,0:48:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And we aren't going to use an
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.60,0:48:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,entry level configuration here
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.39,0:48:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because our implementation is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.84,0:48:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,going to offer up to 11
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.99,0:48:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,teraflops of single precision
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.71,0:48:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,compute power.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.88,0:48:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's three times more than the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.26,0:48:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,best GPU in the Mac Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.94,0:48:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it actually gets even better
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.02,0:48:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because this Radeon Vega GPU can
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.68,0:48:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,also do half precision compute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.88,0:48:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means the iMac Pro can
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.28,0:48:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,deliver up to 22 teraflops of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.54,0:48:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,half precision computation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.47,0:48:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really big deal for
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.89,0:48:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,things like machine learning
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.09,0:48:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,development.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.13,0:48:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So the iMac Pro as you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.53,0:48:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to be a monster when it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.79,0:48:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,comes to graphics, but we didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.35,0:48:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,want to stop there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.70,0:48:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to let you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.40,0:48:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,configure it with up to 128
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.38,0:48:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,gigabytes of ECC memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.43,0:48:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's twice what you can do on
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.81,0:48:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a standard 27-inch iMac.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.52,0:48:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.99,0:49:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And up to 4 terabytes of 3
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.28,0:49:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,gigabyte per second SSD.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.31,0:49:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the iMac Pro is also going
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.23,0:49:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a full complement of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.47,0:49:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,high performance I/O including
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.21,0:49:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,four Thunderbolt 3 ports and for
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.21,0:49:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time ever in any Mac,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.72,0:49:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,built-in 10 gigabit Ethernet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.52,0:49:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.71,0:49:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And with all that cutting edge
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.78,0:49:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I/O, you can do some pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.06,0:49:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,amazing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.79,0:49:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can hook up two 5K
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.85,0:49:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,displays in two high-performance
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.57,0:49:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,RAID arrays, no iMac before
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.22,0:49:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,could ever do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.29,0:49:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you combine that with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.32,0:49:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the internal display, that means
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.10,0:49:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the iMac Pro can drive up to 44
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.90,0:49:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,million pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.24,0:49:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.03,0:49:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even have time to get
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.86,0:49:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,into things like a 1080p
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.57,0:49:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,FaceTime camera, a user
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.87,0:49:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,configurable VESA mount option,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.90,0:49:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,two times wider AVX instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.96,0:49:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and even a UHS-II SD card slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.22,0:49:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So with all these
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.22,0:49:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,high-performance technologies
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.50,0:49:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and our incredible 5K display,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.59,0:49:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this iMac Pro is going to be an
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.02,0:49:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,awesome workstation for things
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.48,0:49:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,like real-time 3D rendering,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.61,0:49:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,high frame rate, immersive VR,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.77,0:50:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,machine learning development,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.71,0:50:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and with all those cores and all
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.51,0:50:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that memory, super fast code
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.22,0:50:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,compiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.13,0:50:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now speaking of workstations, we
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.83,0:50:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to compare the starting
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.23,0:50:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,configuration of the iMac Pro to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.08,0:50:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what's on the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.48,0:50:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, if you were to go out
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.64,0:50:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and build a comparably spec
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.23,0:50:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,system today, it will cost over
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.50,0:50:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,$7000.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.33,0:50:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And keep in mind, that's a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.15,0:50:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,system that doesn't have our
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.23,0:50:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,best in class 5K display.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.69,0:50:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have the iMac Pro's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.56,0:50:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,incredible all-in-one design.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.02,0:50:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then obviously doesn't run
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.35,0:50:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mac OS.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.41,0:50:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the starting
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.53,0:50:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,configuration of the iMac Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.98,0:50:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to price it at
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.39,0:50:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,just $4999.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.52,0:50:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.45,0:50:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's going to be available
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.54,0:50:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.87,0:50:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a sneak peek at the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.79,0:50:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,iMac Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.53,0:50:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It packs workstation class
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.94,0:50:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,performance into our incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.90,0:50:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,27-inch iMac design with its
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.62,0:50:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,gorgeous 5K display.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.02,0:50:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is going to be the most
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.53,0:50:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,powerful Mac we have ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.85,0:51:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is all of our Mac news
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.36,0:51:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.00,0:51:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, back to Tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.02,0:51:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.05,0:51:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thanks John.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.04,0:51:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.84,0:51:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So many great things happening
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.90,0:51:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.54,0:51:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And John, I agree that iMac Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.97,0:51:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is really badass.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.41,0:51:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, next up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.96,0:51:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about iOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.45,0:51:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.88,0:51:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's best and most
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.51,0:51:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced mobile operating
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.07,0:51:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,system.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.11,0:51:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our customers love the latest
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.13,0:51:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,version, iOS 10, which has an
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.47,0:51:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,industry leading 96% customer
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.60,0:51:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.48,0:51:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's absolutely incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.59,0:51:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that 86% of our customers are
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.01,0:51:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,running iOS 10 and taking
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.32,0:51:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,advantages of its capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.41,0:51:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This blows away the other
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.89,0:51:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,platforms that suffer from
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.53,0:51:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,horrible fragmentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.52,0:52:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.13,0:52:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With iOS, developers can always
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.47,0:52:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,target the latest capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.97,0:52:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and features of our latest
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.16,0:52:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,operating system and be
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.96,0:52:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,confident that there's customers
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.96,0:52:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.44,0:52:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now today, we're going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.34,0:52:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's best and most
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.21,0:52:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced mobile operating system
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.64,0:52:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn it up to 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.52,0:52:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.69,0:52:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to invite Craig
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.30,0:52:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,back to take you through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.89,0:52:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Craig?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.02,0:52:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.11,0:52:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you, Tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.25,0:52:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.55,0:52:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about iOS 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.80,0:52:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.61,0:52:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we have a big focus on
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.25,0:52:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,technologies in iOS 11 but also
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.87,0:52:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,some really big features.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.68,0:52:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a lot to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.52,0:52:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to start with
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.96,0:52:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.19,0:53:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you all know in iOS 10, we
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.45,0:53:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,had iMessage apps and stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.18,0:53:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,People had a lot of fun with
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.37,0:53:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,these.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.73,0:53:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And now in iOS 11, we're making
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.39,0:53:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,them more discoverable and ever
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.77,0:53:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with this redesigned app drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.56,0:53:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see you have your apps
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.88,0:53:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,accessible right there at the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.06,0:53:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom of the screen with just a
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.27,0:53:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,tap, you can bring them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.10,0:53:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,scroll through them and tap into
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.11,0:53:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,any app.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.12,0:53:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.02,0:53:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to make it a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.28,0:53:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,fun for you to use your apps and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.85,0:53:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.59,0:53:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the big story with messages
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.36,0:53:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,though is messages in iCloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.75,0:53:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now with your iMessages
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.66,0:53:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and iCloud, when you sign in to
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.18,0:53:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,another new device, well all of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.40,0:53:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,your conversations are
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.61,0:53:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically synchronized.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.52,0:53:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.27,0:53:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, they stay in sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.48,0:53:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you want to delete an
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.40,0:53:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,embarrassing message that you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.54,0:53:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want in your transcript,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.71,0:53:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,well it goes away everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.80,0:53:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,which is kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.44,0:53:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this, of course, allows us
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.97,0:53:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to optimize your device storage
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.45,0:53:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because with your messages in
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.47,0:53:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the cloud, we only need to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.87,0:53:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,your most recent messages cached
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.75,0:54:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on the device and so that makes
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.10,0:54:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for smaller and faster backups
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.30,0:54:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that is available for iOS and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.39,0:54:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.20,0:54:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, your messages
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.37,0:54:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,remain end-to-end encrypted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.68,0:54:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Apple Pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.81,0:54:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So we love using Apple Pay to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.76,0:54:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,buy things at retail.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.15,0:54:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, Apple Pay is the number
