Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.07,0:56:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.12,0:56:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, Siri is a great new
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.12,0:56:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,visual interface as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.53,0:56:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's able to provide you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.56,0:56:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with followup questions and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.19,0:56:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,answers with just a tap and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.60,0:56:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,multiple results.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.11,0:56:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you make a query, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.76,0:56:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,really handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.80,0:56:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Siri also has a new
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.02,0:56:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,capability, just translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.83,0:56:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can now ask something
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.14,0:56:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,like, how do you say what are
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.73,0:56:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the most popular dishes in your
