Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.61,0:56:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And Siri can say,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.52,0:56:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Foreign Language ]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.15,0:56:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.52,0:57:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.40,0:57:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, translation initially will
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.76,0:57:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,support translation from English
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.17,0:57:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to Chinese, French, German,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.12,0:57:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Italian, and Spanish and we'll
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.93,0:57:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,have more language combinations
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.60,0:57:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,coming in the months to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.80,0:57:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when it comes to using Siri
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.44,0:57:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to access your other
