Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.64,0:57:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And SiriKit can now do more than
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.68,0:57:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,ever in iOS 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.36,0:57:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, you can do task
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.20,0:57:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,management by using Siri to make
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.25,0:57:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,tasks and OmniFocus your things,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.85,0:57:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,take notes in Evernote, do
