Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.01,0:57:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,bring up a QR code in WeChat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.10,0:57:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Siri isn't just a voice
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.43,0:57:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,assistant, because with Siri
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.75,0:57:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Intelligence, Siri not only
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.64,0:57:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,understands your voice, it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.09,0:57:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,understands the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.12,0:57:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It understands your interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.24,0:57:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It understands how you use your
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.43,0:57:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,device.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.91,0:57:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And this allows it to ultimately
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.15,0:57:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,understand what you want next.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.89,0:57:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we've all experienced this
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.73,0:57:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,where Siri can help us predict
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.31,0:58:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what apps we might want to use
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.75,0:58:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,next, give us a time to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.14,0:58:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,notification based on our
