Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.98,0:58:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,us respond to a text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.98,0:58:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In iOS 11, Siri uses on-device
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.64,0:58:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,learning to understand more
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.10,0:58:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,about topics of interest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.27,0:58:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So it can actually suggest
