Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.05,0:58:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.02,0:58:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And even help us make a calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.58,0:58:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,appointment based on something
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.65,0:58:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we've just booked inside of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.90,0:58:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Safari on the web.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.91,0:58:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And what Siri learns about you
