Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.51,0:58:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're dealing with one Siri
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.87,0:58:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but of course this is kept
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.32,0:58:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,completely private, readable
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.96,0:58:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,only by you and your devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.52,0:58:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.66,0:58:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's talk about the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.27,0:58:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.58,0:58:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People love the fantastic
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.80,0:58:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,cameras in the iPhone 7 and 7
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.76,0:58:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.16,0:59:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And in fact, our customers now
