Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.13,0:59:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,means less storage space used on
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.94,0:59:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,your device and less space used
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.17,0:59:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the cloud.
