Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.97,1:16:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,better store for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.99,1:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's many things we can talk
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.12,1:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,about but I think one stands
