Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.56,1:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see how customers are
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.75,1:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,responding to that update.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.60,1:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's really great feature for
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.09,1:16:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you to take advantage of.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.09,1:16:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.62,1:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,coming this year but there is
