Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.49,1:27:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship to the light here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.28,1:27:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.40,1:27:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I can add additional
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.11,1:27:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,objects.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.64,1:27:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's add a vase to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.00,1:27:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, isn't that just
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.71,1:27:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,incredible?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.04,1:27:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you guys are actually in
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.11,1:27:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the shot here with these objects
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.48,1:27:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,all in augment reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.89,1:27:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So it gives you a little bit of
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.84,1:27:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,an idea of the technology
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.91,1:27:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.42,1:27:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.03,1:27:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how do we do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.52,1:27:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.18,1:27:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, ARKit provides fast and
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.23,1:27:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,stable motion tracking and it
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.91,1:27:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,uses all of the sensors and the
