Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.30,1:27:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,this.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.86,1:27:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It actually finds planes like
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.58,1:27:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,floors and tables.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.94,1:27:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's able to estimate ambient
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.98,1:27:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,light which helps us with the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.53,1:27:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,rendering and also helps with
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.86,1:27:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.15,1:27:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice that cup hit the
