Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.56,1:27:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,frameworks to help you with your
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.64,1:27:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,rendering.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.49,1:27:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The implementation is possible
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.67,1:27:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're able to take
