Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.62,1:28:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,millions of iPhones and iPads
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.63,1:28:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that are going to be capable of
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.62,1:28:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,AR.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.05,1:28:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And, in fact, that's going to
