Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.90,1:29:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know Peter Jackson from
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.35,1:29:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,his incredible cinematic work on
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.29,1:29:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,movies like The Lord of the
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.14,1:29:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rings series.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.94,1:29:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's now really excited
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.78,1:29:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,about AR.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.35,1:29:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And to show you what he has in
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.76,1:29:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the works, I'm thrilled to
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.66,1:29:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,introduce Wingnut AR's creative
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.87,1:29:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,director, Alasdair Coull.
