Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.52,1:29:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.31,1:29:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thanks, Craig.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.93,1:29:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really excited to share an
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.61,1:29:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,exclusive sneak peek of
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.75,1:29:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,something we've been working on.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.09,1:30:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,With the ARKit, you don't need
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.21,1:30:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,any special equipment or
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.09,1:30:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,tracking markers, it just works.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.48,1:30:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dan is here with me for Wingnut
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.53,1:30:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,AR, so let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.00,1:30:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we're using ARKit to detect
