Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.95,1:30:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,get repairs and to trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.28,1:30:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our townsfolk.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.33,1:30:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're expecting some visitors
