Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.03,1:33:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,boundaries on iPad.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.91,1:34:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, we're going to push
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.19,1:34:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,them further than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.77,1:34:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And to tell you all about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.94,1:34:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to invite up Joz.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.48,1:34:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Joz
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.52,1:34:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.71,1:34:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you, Tim.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.09,1:34:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And good morning, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.10,1:34:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited to talk to you
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.48,1:34:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,today about iPad Pro.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.19,1:34:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When we first introduced iPad
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.94,1:34:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro just 18 months ago, it
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.07,1:34:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,completely redefined what you
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.39,1:34:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,could do with your iPad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.86,1:34:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with your incredible apps,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.55,1:34:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it allowed our users to do
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.72,1:34:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,really amazing things, from
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.77,1:34:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,professional design and
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.05,1:34:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,illustration to fashion, to
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.16,1:34:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,architecture, to engineering and
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.82,1:34:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so much more.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.73,1:34:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really excited about what
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.43,1:34:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,can be real in your world today
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.72,1:34:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with iPad Pro.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.80,1:34:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as you know, there's two
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.93,1:34:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,models to iPad Pro today.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.21,1:34:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a 13-inch and a
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.23,1:34:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,9.7-inch.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.67,1:34:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And the 9.7-inch is our most
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.38,1:34:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,popular model.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.79,1:34:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a screen large enough to
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.30,1:34:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,get your work done, but it's in
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.78,1:34:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,a thin and light enough package
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.15,1:35:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that allows you to take it with
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.35,1:35:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you everywhere you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.52,1:35:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, today, we're going to
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.64,1:35:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,introduce an all new iPad Pro.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.36,1:35:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to take everything
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.25,1:35:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you love about the 9.7-inch and
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.97,1:35:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,give you a whole lot more to
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.00,1:35:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,love.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.78,1:35:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.60,1:35:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the new iPad Pro.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.52,1:35:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.70,1:35:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first iPad Pro with a
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.14,1:35:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,larger 10 and a half inch Retina
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.11,1:35:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,display.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.73,1:35:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why 10 and a half inch?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.57,1:35:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for one, it's a lot
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.68,1:35:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,larger.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.38,1:35:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 20% larger than a 9.7-inch.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.07,1:35:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we are able to reduce the
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.31,1:35:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,borders by nearly 40% which
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.00,1:35:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,allows us to submit it in this
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.44,1:35:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,incredibly compact design that
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.54,1:35:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,still weighs just one pound.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.59,1:35:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, 10.5-inch also
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.46,1:35:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,allows us to do some other
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.47,1:35:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,things.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.15,1:35:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect size to allow
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.18,1:35:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,us to display a full-size
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.01,1:35:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,on-screen keyboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.52,1:35:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.67,1:35:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also the perfect size to
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.17,1:36:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,allow us to have a full-size
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.53,1:36:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Smart keyboard as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.26,1:36:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we deliver the Smart
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.31,1:36:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,keyboard, we're going to have
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.17,1:36:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,support for more than 30
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.65,1:36:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,languages at launch including
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.58,1:36:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese, and for the very first
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.42,1:36:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,time, a Japanese JIS keyboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.52,1:36:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.51,1:36:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, iPad Pro has always had the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.64,1:36:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,best displays in the industry.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.71,1:36:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And both sizes are going to get
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.27,1:36:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,really incredible new displays
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.95,1:36:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,today.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.09,1:36:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the best displays that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.99,1:36:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we've ever made.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.00,1:36:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're packed with incredible
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.08,1:36:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,features like True Tone for
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.25,1:36:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,automatic white balance, P3 wide
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.87,1:36:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,color gamut for the best color,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.75,1:36:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ultralow reflectivity, the best
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.74,1:36:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the industry.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.47,1:36:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're 50% brighter with
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.07,1:36:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,600 nits.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.47,1:36:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And this extra brightness and
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.23,1:36:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the P3 wide color gamut means
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.55,1:36:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that with iOS 11, you'll be able
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.01,1:36:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to display HDR video for the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.09,1:36:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,first time in an iPad for really
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.26,1:36:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,immersive cinematic experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.44,1:36:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're truly awesome displays.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.62,1:36:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But our biggest breakthrough is
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.75,1:37:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a feature we call ProMotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.37,1:37:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is ProMotion?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.73,1:37:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we were able to take our
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.03,1:37:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,unique hardware and software
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.33,1:37:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,capabilities and dramatically
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.75,1:37:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,improve our display performance.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.39,1:37:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, typically, up until today,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.84,1:37:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,mobile displays have refresh at
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.51,1:37:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,60 hertz, means they update the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.75,1:37:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,content 60 times every second.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.43,1:37:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, on the new iPad Pro, we've
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.45,1:37:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,doubled that maximum refresh
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.02,1:37:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,rate to an incredible 120 hertz.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.52,1:37:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.14,1:37:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does that mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.33,1:37:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that all of your motion
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.79,1:37:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,content on your screen is going
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.90,1:37:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to be smoother, crisper, more
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.70,1:37:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,responsive.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.31,1:37:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is something you have
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.19,1:37:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to really touch and feel
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.20,1:37:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself to appreciate because
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.80,1:37:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,our projection systems just
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.08,1:37:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't capable of doing those
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.29,1:37:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,type of refresh rates.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.73,1:37:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you the difference
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.90,1:37:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.71,1:37:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you scroll, it's
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.45,1:37:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,buttery smooth.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.45,1:37:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the higher refresh rate
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.74,1:37:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,also means it works even better
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.47,1:37:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Apple Pencil.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.70,1:37:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We already have the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.84,1:38:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,industry-leading performance for
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.37,1:38:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,drawing and writing with the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.73,1:38:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Pencil, but with
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.73,1:38:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ProMotion, it gets even better.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.21,1:38:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more responsive and it
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.52,1:38:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,reduces our latency to an
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.94,1:38:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,industry best 20 milliseconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.52,1:38:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.33,1:38:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So drawing is incredibly fluid
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.21,1:38:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and even more natural, you're
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.63,1:38:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,going to love using the Apple
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.49,1:38:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pencil of the new iPad Pro.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.44,1:38:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Another breakthrough of
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.45,1:38:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ProMotion is that these become
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.08,1:38:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the first mobile displays to be
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.52,1:38:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,able to dynamically adjust the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.27,1:38:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,refresh rate, depending on what
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.93,1:38:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you're looking at.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.96,1:38:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really big
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.97,1:38:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,breakthrough for both display
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.17,1:38:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,quality, as well as for power
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.42,1:38:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,savings.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.36,1:38:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you have dash-moving
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.69,1:38:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,content, they can update
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.83,1:38:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.06,1:38:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But they can also update slower
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.27,1:38:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when you don't need that type of
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.52,1:38:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,refresh rate.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.02,1:38:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, a still image, this
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.82,1:38:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,allows us to save a lot of
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.89,1:38:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,energy and give you better
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.93,1:38:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,battery life.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.41,1:38:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hopefully you see why these
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.61,1:38:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,are not just the best displays
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.18,1:38:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've ever made, but we
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.01,1:38:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,think they're the most advanced
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.03,1:38:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,displays in the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.52,1:38:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's talk about
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.51,1:38:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,performance.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.30,1:39:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,iPad is already best in class
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.30,1:39:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,for performance.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.44,1:39:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not resting on our
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.47,1:39:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,laurels.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.66,1:39:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the fastest we've ever
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.41,1:39:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,created.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.50,1:39:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside them, they're powered by
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.07,1:39:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the A10X Fusion chip.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.76,1:39:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The A10X has a six-core CPU,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.55,1:39:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,three high-performance cores,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.22,1:39:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,three high-efficiency cores, all
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.72,1:39:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically managed by the
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.41,1:39:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple performance controller.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.83,1:39:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It also has a 12-core GPU.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.68,1:39:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a powerhouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.12,1:39:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And it delivers 30% faster CPU
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.95,1:39:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,performance over our already
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.93,1:39:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,industry leading A9X and 40%
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.67,1:39:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,faster graphics performance.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.52,1:39:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.60,1:39:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our chip team has done just an
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.42,1:39:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,amazing job over the years with
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.65,1:39:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the performance improvements and
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.81,1:39:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,results have been staggering.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.55,1:39:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're delivering an
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.15,1:39:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,industry-leading graphics
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.38,1:39:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,performance that's more than 500
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.60,1:39:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,times the original iPad from
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.09,1:39:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,just a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.87,1:40:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, numbers only tell
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.64,1:40:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,part of the story.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.19,1:40:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To demonstrate the real-world
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.40,1:40:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,performance of the A10X in the
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.78,1:40:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,new iPad Pro, I'd like to invite
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.90,1:40:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ash Hewson of Serif to give you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.51,1:40:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a demo of their new Pro photo
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.94,1:40:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,editing app called Affinity
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.48,1:40:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.90,1:40:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ash.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.02,1:40:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.01,1:40:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thanks, Joz.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.93,1:40:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm thrilled today to be able
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.99,1:40:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to show you the iPad version of
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.40,1:40:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Affinity Photo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.77,1:40:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a truly high-end
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.13,1:40:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,professional photo editing tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.26,1:40:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And on this latest iPad Pro, we
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.31,1:40:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,can achieve levels of
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.12,1:40:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,performance which is simply
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.68,1:40:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,unattainable on any other
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.79,1:40:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,device.
