Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.29,1:53:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,integrated it deeply into the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.98,1:53:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,system.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.92,1:53:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it starts with markup,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.12,1:53:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because you can mark up anything
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.81,1:53:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you can Quick Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.16,1:53:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take Safari content,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.96,1:53:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,recreate it into a continuous
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.46,1:53:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,scrolling view that you can mark
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.43,1:53:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.76,1:53:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can actually do this
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.74,1:53:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with any app that supports
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.21,1:53:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,printing, because we have a
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.26,1:53:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,create PDF option that will
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.21,1:53:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,create a markup PDF, it's a
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.99,1:53:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,really great way to mark up
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.04,1:53:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,anything and share it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.84,1:53:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We know, a lot of people do like
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.92,1:53:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to share with screenshots, and
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.11,1:53:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so now when you take a
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.06,1:53:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,screenshot, we'll create a
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.79,1:53:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,thumbnail down in the bottom of
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.04,1:53:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.31,1:53:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tap it, you go instantly
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.36,1:53:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in the markup, you can mark it
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.51,1:53:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,up right there and share it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.85,1:53:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we've all-- It's really
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.75,1:53:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.52,1:53:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.09,1:53:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we've also integrated
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.36,1:53:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pencil deeply into Notes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.80,1:53:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're working on a note
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.08,1:53:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and later you're at the lock
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.22,1:53:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,screen, you want to get back,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.22,1:53:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,just a tap of the pencil to lock
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.81,1:53:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,screen and your right back into
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.62,1:53:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,your note.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.69,1:53:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've made your note
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.97,1:54:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,handwritten text searchable.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.03,1:54:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can now search handwriting
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.48,1:54:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and we use deep learning to
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.62,1:54:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize what you write.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.90,1:54:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're doing primarily
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.02,1:54:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,typed notes, you can now also do
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.01,1:54:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,inline drawings, right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.24,1:54:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very handy.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.05,1:54:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.08,1:54:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now of course, sometimes we
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.34,1:54:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,still have to deal with paper,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.87,1:54:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so Notes now has a built-in
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.67,1:54:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,document scanner.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.80,1:54:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It can correct perspective and
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.76,1:54:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,contrast.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.01,1:54:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you bring the note in,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.35,1:54:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you can mark it up, write with
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.66,1:54:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,your pencil.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.25,1:54:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.48,1:54:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've integrated markup in
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.34,1:54:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the mail as well so you can
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.62,1:54:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,personalize your mail messages
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.45,1:54:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,with the inline drawings.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.42,1:54:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for a look at all of these
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.38,1:54:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,great new Pencil features, I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.26,1:54:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,like to introduce the man who
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.81,1:54:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,heads iPad software engineering
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.81,1:54:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for us, Toby Paterson, for a
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.61,1:54:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,live demo.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.57,1:54:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Toby.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.35,1:54:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.68,1:54:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.19,1:54:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.37,1:54:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the first thing I want to
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.31,1:55:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,show you is a quick way of
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.05,1:55:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,getting to your notes using your
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.03,1:55:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Pencil.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.74,1:55:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You just tap on the lock screen
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.21,1:55:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,like this and it slides up to
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.57,1:55:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,reveal your notes beneath it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.73,1:55:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can see here I've got a
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.05,1:55:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,handwritten note and I want to
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.55,1:55:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,show you how easy it is to
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.94,1:55:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,create one of these.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.04,1:55:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch at the top of the note
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.21,1:55:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,here as I edit the title.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.92,1:55:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by putting the pencil down
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.86,1:55:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and writing like this, after the
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.06,1:55:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,2017 keynote.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.22,1:55:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as natural as putting
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.53,1:55:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,pencil to paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.16,1:55:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now something paper can't help
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.63,1:55:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you with is finding your notes
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.99,1:55:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,again later.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.28,1:55:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're using machine learning to
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.64,1:55:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize your handwriting and
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.67,1:55:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,index it in Spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.94,1:55:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's switch into Spotlight now
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.32,1:55:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll search for that text
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.99,1:55:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that I just wrote down.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.82,1:55:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see here I've got the
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.75,1:55:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,new flick keyboard which makes
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.31,1:55:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it really easy to enter numbers
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.38,1:55:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,just by swiping down on the keys
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.47,1:55:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.93,1:55:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see there it's
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.89,1:55:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,already found my note as the top
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.59,1:56:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,hit even with my atrocious
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.45,1:56:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.89,1:56:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just tap on that and we're
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.86,1:56:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,back with the note.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.50,1:56:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.99,1:56:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm going to switch to a
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.60,1:56:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,different note now, because I
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.85,1:56:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,want to show you how you can mix
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.07,1:56:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,drawing with typed text and
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.12,1:56:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,tables and all of the notes'
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.48,1:56:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,other great features.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.29,1:56:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a note that my young
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.48,1:56:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,daughter shared with me as part
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.83,1:56:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of a school assignment where she
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.83,1:56:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,had to work with her parents to
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.09,1:56:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,develop an idea for a new app.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.70,1:56:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she asked me how many
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.89,1:56:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,copies of our app I thought I
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.35,1:56:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,might sell-- We might sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.38,1:56:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I want to quickly draw a
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.98,1:56:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,graph to give her some idea of
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.06,1:56:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.15,1:56:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to press down
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.99,1:56:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,here with the pencil to make
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.12,1:56:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,some space for my drawing and
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.58,1:56:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,then we can take that little
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.54,1:56:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,grabber and open up some more
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.45,1:56:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.07,1:56:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I am really bad at drawing
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.80,1:56:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just love doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.78,1:56:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's great about drawing
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.03,1:56:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on the iPad is it works the same
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.96,1:56:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,way as it does with paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.38,1:56:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And that means it's really easy
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.40,1:56:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to draw really badly
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.39,1:56:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.65,1:57:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch. I'm just going to put the
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.97,1:57:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,pencil down and just like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.54,1:57:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,zoom.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.49,1:57:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so simple, and I think
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.94,1:57:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to have a lot of
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.38,1:57:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,fun rediscovering the joy of
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.92,1:57:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,drawing.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.97,1:57:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's move on now.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.88,1:57:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my daughter's learned a few
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.00,1:57:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,things from me about how Apple
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.27,1:57:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,works.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.65,1:57:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And before I left this morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.28,1:57:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she gave me an NDA to sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.15,1:57:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use the new
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.90,1:57:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,document scanner notes and my
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.62,1:57:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,pencil to take care of that in a
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.57,1:57:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,snap.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.11,1:57:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just tap the plus button
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.22,1:57:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,here to bring up the document
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.46,1:57:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,scanner and all I need to do is
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.54,1:57:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,point the camera at the piece of
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.34,1:57:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.37,1:57:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Notes will take the picture
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.58,1:57:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically, even straighten
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.83,1:57:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the page up.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.81,1:57:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll open it up full screen
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.19,1:57:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,here and I just fill in the
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.87,1:57:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,blanks with my pencil.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.44,1:57:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And just like that, I've got a
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.57,1:57:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,signed copy of the NDA saved
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.91,1:57:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,away in my notes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.74,1:57:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see my daughter sent me a
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.13,1:57:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,message and it must be pretty
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.38,1:57:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,important if she's interrupting
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.68,1:57:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,my demo.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.16,1:58:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you'll excuse me, I'm just
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.92,1:58:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,going to tap on that and see
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.95,1:58:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what she has to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.93,1:58:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, an offer for $100 million
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.51,1:58:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is really pretty thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.52,1:58:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to send this to my wife
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.26,1:58:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.10,1:58:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a screenshot
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.66,1:58:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of this and then we'll tap on
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.54,1:58:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the thumbnail here to open up
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.36,1:58:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,our new screenshot editing UI.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.16,1:58:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, I can crop it down to
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.20,1:58:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,just the part of the image that
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.93,1:58:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to send.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.70,1:58:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can scribble a quick note with
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.87,1:58:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,my pencil, and then I can bring
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.14,1:58:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,up the share sheet to send it
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.03,1:58:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,off to my wife right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.70,1:58:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are just a few of the
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.94,1:58:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ways you can use your pencil
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.17,1:58:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with your iPad in iOS 11.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.55,1:58:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to you now, Craig.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.52,1:58:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.52,1:58:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.07,1:58:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It is so great when your
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.57,1:58:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,grade school child gets $100
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.98,1:58:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,million of funding.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.05,1:58:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They just-- They do grow up so
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.02,1:58:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,fast these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.91,1:58:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so these are some of the
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.83,1:59:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,great new features for the iPad
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.12,1:59:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course they're joined by
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.31,1:59:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,all of these other features you
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.78,1:59:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,heard from earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.01,1:59:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really excited about what
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.56,1:59:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we're doing with iPad this year,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.91,1:59:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and really excited about iOS 11.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.71,1:59:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now iOS 11 is available to all
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.81,1:59:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of you, developers, today.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.03,1:59:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you sign up at
