Dialogue: 0,2:08:35.50,2:08:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,instrumentation and direct that
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.34,2:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the room as well.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.52,2:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Music ]
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.09,2:08:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to that direct
Dialogue: 0,2:08:49.99,2:08:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,energy, there's something that's
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.52,2:08:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,usually missing in music,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.75,2:08:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,ambient audio, the backing
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.06,2:08:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,vocals and reverb.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:56.52,2:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Music ]
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.04,2:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,HomePod can direct all of these
Dialogue: 0,2:09:07.61,2:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and pull it together to a full
Dialogue: 0,2:09:09.31,2:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,rich mix that fills up your
Dialogue: 0,2:09:11.02,2:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.52,2:09:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Music ]
Dialogue: 0,2:09:23.52,2:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.99,2:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really remarkable
Dialogue: 0,2:09:30.13,2:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,experience to hear this kind of
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.45,2:09:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a spacious sound come from such
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.33,2:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a compact speaker.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.36,2:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you love one, you should
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.51,2:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,see what it's like when you set
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.61,2:09:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,up two and they automatically
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.13,2:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,work together to give this
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.24,2:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,incredible spacious sound that
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.10,2:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,really has the power to rock
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.77,2:09:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,your house.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:44.93,2:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, a musicologist.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:48.42,2:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This intelligent helper to help
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.40,2:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,us discover the music we love.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:53.54,2:09:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,HomePod has an incredible
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.96,2:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,speaker system that works
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.32,2:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,together with our Apple Music
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.56,2:10:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,subscription.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.25,2:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning, it's
Dialogue: 0,2:10:02.36,2:10:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,designed to work with that.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.08,2:10:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Apple Music as you know
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.65,2:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,provides music in the cloud and
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.32,2:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,if the speaker can get it
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.18,2:10:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,directly from the cloud, it can
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.37,2:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,get 40 million tracks, two
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.17,2:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,million artists, tens of
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.12,2:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,thousands of playlists.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:14.18,2:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But not just any music library,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.76,2:10:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this is your music library.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.39,2:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It knows the playlists you've
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.54,2:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,set up, it knows the artist you
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.01,2:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,love and all of them stream
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.85,2:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,directly to your HomePod.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.85,2:10:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It works with an array of six
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.09,2:10:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,microphones around the middle,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.49,2:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so as you talk to it and you say
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.54,2:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,those magic words, "Hey Siri,"
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.06,2:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you see a waveform light up on
Dialogue: 0,2:10:35.54,2:10:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,top and now it can respond to
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.56,2:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,your commands and help serve up
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.10,2:10:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the music you want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.74,2:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Siri team has worked very
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.33,2:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,hard to adapt the domain of
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.40,2:10:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,music in Siri to be even greater
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.39,2:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and understand more of the
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.16,2:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,questions we're going to ask
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.31,2:10:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,about music.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.21,2:10:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple things obviously like
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.60,2:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Play Beats 1 Radio.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.24,2:10:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We all want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.43,2:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or play "I'm Poppy".
Dialogue: 0,2:10:58.24,2:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out if you don't know
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.22,2:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what that's about.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:01.03,2:11:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Play something new.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.33,2:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's singing on this track?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.49,2:11:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I ask all the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.58,2:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's playing drums on this
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.76,2:11:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,track?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.42,2:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To complex questions like, what
Dialogue: 0,2:11:07.85,2:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,was the top song on May 5th,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.74,2:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,2016.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.44,2:11:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You just play more like that or
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.34,2:11:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that song.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:15.24,2:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a free form.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.41,2:11:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Siri doesn't need a specific
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.89,2:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,list of commands.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:18.53,2:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It can interpret what you're
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.82,2:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,saying and help you discover the
Dialogue: 0,2:11:21.75,2:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,music you love.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.23,2:11:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And even better, you don't have
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.59,2:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to just sit next to the HomePod
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.70,2:11:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to talk to it.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.43,2:11:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be across the room and
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.45,2:11:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,speak to the HomePod even while
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.05,2:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,loud music is playing and the
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.64,2:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,speaker array and the
Dialogue: 0,2:11:33.48,2:11:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,microphones can pick it up and
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.16,2:11:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,hear what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.20,2:11:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So HomePod, it has the power to
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.82,2:11:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,rock the house in a spatial
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.12,2:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness so that it understands
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.48,2:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the rooms we place it within.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.31,2:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has the fun interactivity
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.74,2:11:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of Siri becoming a musicologist
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.84,2:11:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and helping us to listen to the
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.18,2:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,music we love.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.98,2:11:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And since Siri is built in there
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.87,2:11:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can speak to it, well,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.37,2:11:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the team has also worked hard to
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.55,2:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,make it a great and helpful home
Dialogue: 0,2:11:58.48,2:11:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,assistant as well.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.97,2:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We said the domain of music is
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.32,2:12:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,something Siri knows really well
Dialogue: 0,2:12:04.64,2:12:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in HomePod.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.30,2:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other domains as well.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.26,2:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've worked hard to pick the
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.40,2:12:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,first ones that we think matter
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.71,2:12:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,most in a product like HomePod,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.35,2:12:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so of course, it can play your
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.64,2:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,podcasts.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:13.27,2:12:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it can also do things like
Dialogue: 0,2:12:15.74,2:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,give you news, give you weather,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.63,2:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,traffic, sports.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:18.90,2:12:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask it to set a
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.21,2:12:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,reminder, set a timer, text
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.29,2:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,someone with messages.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.88,2:12:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you have HomeKit devices
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.44,2:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,set up in your home, you can
Dialogue: 0,2:12:27.45,2:12:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,speak to your HomePod and
Dialogue: 0,2:12:28.78,2:12:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,control your HomeKit devices.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.18,2:12:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example, for the HomePod
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.72,2:12:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,set up, you can say, "When do
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.64,2:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the Red Sox play next?"
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.05,2:12:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to beat the
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.10,2:12:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yankees, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:40.70,2:12:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tune to NPR instead, flip a
Dialogue: 0,2:12:43.84,2:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,coin, remind me to bring snacks
Dialogue: 0,2:12:45.60,2:12:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to a party.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:46.81,2:12:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can set up reminders, check
Dialogue: 0,2:12:49.11,2:12:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,all the sports news and weather,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.01,2:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all directly with your voice,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.66,2:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,talk to a HomePod that gets the
Dialogue: 0,2:12:53.85,2:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,information directly from the
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.50,2:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,cloud.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:56.00,2:12:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you have HomeKit devices
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.20,2:12:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,set up, you can say simple
Dialogue: 0,2:12:59.83,2:13:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,things like, are the lights on,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:01.90,2:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,turn the heat up, turn on the
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.78,2:13:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,air conditioning, bring the
Dialogue: 0,2:13:05.40,2:13:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,shades down halfway, turn off
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.03,2:13:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the lights in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:10.08,2:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you've set up scenes in
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.47,2:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,HomeKit you can control those as
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.74,2:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,well.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:13.36,2:13:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say, "I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.15,2:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's movie time.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.04,2:13:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now."
Dialogue: 0,2:13:17.47,2:13:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole scene can
Dialogue: 0,2:13:18.70,2:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically happen just by
Dialogue: 0,2:13:21.00,2:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to your HomePod.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:23.13,2:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And because there is a HomePod
Dialogue: 0,2:13:26.37,2:13:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,base-- the HomeKit base built
Dialogue: 0,2:13:27.76,2:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,into HomePod, that means
Dialogue: 0,2:13:29.45,2:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere in the world, once you
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.90,2:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,set up your first HomePod, you
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.29,2:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,control your HomeKit devices
Dialogue: 0,2:13:34.12,2:13:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,remotely using the built-in Home
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.91,2:13:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,app on your iPhone or iPad.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:38.07,2:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, setting up a HomePod and
Dialogue: 0,2:13:41.27,2:13:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,its microphone array in your
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.89,2:13:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,home, you probably have a
Dialogue: 0,2:13:44.02,2:13:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,question that we've worked
Dialogue: 0,2:13:45.31,2:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,really hard to deal with, which
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.74,2:13:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is privacy.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.05,2:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our team cares deeply about your
Dialogue: 0,2:13:49.92,2:13:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,privacy.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.11,2:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example, it has that
Dialogue: 0,2:13:53.00,2:13:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,magic phrase, hey Siri.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:54.66,2:13:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you say it, nothing is
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.78,2:13:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,being sent to Apple.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.87,2:14:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It recognizes when you do say it
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.76,2:14:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and from that point it sends an
Dialogue: 0,2:14:02.09,2:14:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,anonymous Siri ID in order to
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.37,2:14:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,help you with the command you're
Dialogue: 0,2:14:05.50,2:14:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:06.12,2:14:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course that communication
Dialogue: 0,2:14:08.25,2:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is all encrypted.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.91,2:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the HomePod.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:12.85,2:14:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a breakthrough home
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.11,2:14:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,speaker.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:16.26,2:14:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Typically Wi-Fi speakers, if
Dialogue: 0,2:14:18.18,2:14:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they're a good quality, of $300
Dialogue: 0,2:14:20.76,2:14:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to $500.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.94,2:14:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And a smart speaker might cost
Dialogue: 0,2:14:24.31,2:14:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you $100 to $200.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:27.13,2:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not unreasonable for a
Dialogue: 0,2:14:28.26,2:14:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,HomePod to be priced in the
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.40,2:14:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,range of $400 to $700.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.09,2:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're really excited to tell
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.67,2:14:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you that HomePod is going to be
Dialogue: 0,2:14:36.55,2:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,priced for $349.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.52,2:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,2:14:45.88,2:14:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes in white and space
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.67,2:14:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,gray.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.89,2:14:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll start shipping this
Dialogue: 0,2:14:50.03,2:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,December, first in the US, UK,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:52.70,2:14:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and Australia.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.16,2:14:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then next year we'll start
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.96,2:14:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,bringing it around the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:57.91,2:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's HomePod.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.17,2:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to you, Tim.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.52,2:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause and Cheering ]
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.12,2:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:07.86,2:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.19,2:15:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We really believe it's going to
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.21,2:15:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,take your home music experience
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.56,2:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next level.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:16.41,2:15:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's been an incredible
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.72,2:15:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,morning.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.14,2:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We've shared with you lots of
Dialogue: 0,2:15:22.72,2:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,things this morning and all of
